scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 3-217 comprise the full text of the Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, including all 'Parts' (1-5) and the signature blocks. The content before line 3 is cover/exhibit information, and line 218 is a footer. The Schedule proper starts at line 3 ('SCHEDULE to the 1992 ISDA Master Agreement...') and ends at the execution signatures (line 217). This excludes any standard pre-print, CSA annexes, or other attachments.
